snippet: Rebel fighters have ejected the Islamic State of Iraq and Syria from its headquarters in Aleppo.
abstract: Rebel fighters in Syria eject Islamic State of Iraq and Syria from its headquarters in the major city of Aleppo, dealing Al-Qaeda-linked group a sharp reversal.

byline.contributor: Hwaida Saad and Mohammad Ghannam contributed reporting from Beirut, and Karam Shoumali from Istanbul.
